text: Cecil Reign Taylor Jr. (born October 31, 1933) is a former American football player who played for the Los Angeles Rams of the National Football League (NFL). He played college football at Kansas State University. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Kansas State Wildcats football players Category:Los Angeles Rams players Category:American football defensive backs Category:Players of American football from Missouri Category:Sportspeople from Kansas City, Missouri Category:American football running backs
